# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   See https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv/header#shared-local-install-versions
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in git.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if platform is rather diverse, it may cause trouble
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipenv, poetry.lock is generally recommended to be committed
#   poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipenv, pdm.lock is generally recommended to be committed
#   pdm.lock

